edu.uci.inf111.SelfCheckOut.App
Interface Code

All Known Implementing Classes:
BIC, UPC
public interface Code

The Code interface represents the methods common to Universal Product Codes (UPCs) and Bulk Item Codes (BICs). This allows the two types of codes to be used interchangeably where appropriate.

See Also:
BIC, UPC
